@startuml
skinparam participantBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam lifelineStrategy solid

actor "Người dùng" as User #Yellow
boundary "FrontendApp" as UI #Yellow
boundary "AxiosClient" as API #Yellow
control "AuthController" as Ctrl #Yellow
control "AuthService" as Svc #Yellow
entity "User" as UserEnt #Yellow
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #Yellow

User -> UI : 1: Token hết hạn (HTTP 401)
activate UI
UI -> UI : 1.1: Phát hiện 401 từ interceptor\n(localStorage.removeItem("accessToken")\nwindow.location.href = "/login")
deactivate UI

note right of UI : Luồng refresh token\nđược gọi thủ công

User -> UI : 2: Gọi refresh token
activate UI
UI -> UI : 2.1: Lấy refreshToken từ localStorage
UI -> API : 2.2: POST /api/Auth/refresh\nbody: { refreshToken: "..." }
activate API
API -> Ctrl : 2.3: Chuyển tiếp request
activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Ctrl : 2.4: Chuyển đổi body -> string refreshToken
Ctrl -> Svc : 2.5: RefreshTokenAsync(refreshToken)
activate Svc

Svc -> DB : 2.6: Users.GetQueryable()\n.Include(u => u.UserRoles)\n.ThenInclude(ur => ur.Role)\n.FirstOrDefaultAsync(u => u.RefreshToken == token)
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 2.6.1: User (có Roles) hoặc null
deactivate DB

alt 2.7: [user == null || RefreshTokenExpiry < UtcNow]
Svc --> Ctrl : 2.7.1: ApiResponse.Fail(\n"Invalid or expired refresh token", 401)
Ctrl --> API : 2.7.2: StatusCode(401)
API --> UI : 2.7.3: Response 401
UI -> UI : 2.7.4: Xoá token khỏi localStorage\nChuyển hướng đến /login
UI --> User : 2.7.5: Hiển thị trang đăng nhập
else 2.8: [RefreshToken hợp lệ]
Svc -> Svc : 2.8.1: GenerateJwtToken(user)\n(claims + 24h expiry)
Svc -> Svc : 2.8.2: GenerateRefreshToken()\n(32 bytes random -> Base64)

Svc -> DB : 2.8.3: user.RefreshToken = newRefreshToken\nuser.RefreshTokenExpiry = UtcNow+7d\nSaveChangesAsync()
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 2.8.3.1: OK
deactivate DB

Svc -> Svc : 2.8.4: Tạo LoginResponse mới
Svc --> Ctrl : 2.8.5: ApiResponse.Ok(LoginResponse)
end

deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> API : 2.9: StatusCode(200, ApiResponse<LoginResponse>)
deactivate Ctrl
API --> UI : 2.10: Response JSON (newToken, newRefreshToken)
deactivate API

UI -> UI : 2.11: Cập nhật localStorage:\n- accessToken = newToken\n- refreshToken = newRefreshToken
UI --> User : 2.12: Token đã được làm mới\n(tiếp tục phiên làm việc)
deactivate UI

@enduml
